And in fact, it isn't happening right now. And to be able to then create the ground underneath you to put a reality, a different way of experiencing yourself, you know, that is not fed by all the horrible things that happen to you.

595
01:48:32,000 --> 01:48:35,000
Then that is a part of the trauma healing work.

596
01:48:36,000 --> 01:48:41,000
