01:49:45,000 --> 01:49:48,000
But now that you have a family, this is no longer adaptive.

606
01:49:49,000 --> 01:49:57,000
Yes, I use the word. Generally, it was useful then you badly needed it. But it's not it's not serving you now.

607
01:49:58,000 --> 01:50:03,000
Your reality has changed and you're still holding an umbrella, even though there is no rain.

