635
01:56:43,000 --> 01:56:55,000
Now you're telling me? That instantly is going to do something to my goodwill, let's even put it like that. My ownership, my responsibility, my vulnerability by just putting myself out there.

636
01:56:56,000 --> 01:57:19,000
